% * 50% * 50% = 12.5%。<br><br>所以从实验观测的角度来说，我们要抛足够多的次数，才可能获得更接近理论的值，否则偶然性太大。这些我会在后面的专栏介绍。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"黄申","uid":"1275061","ctime":1548697703,"ip_address":"","comment_id":64058,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"48793293031","product_id":100021201,"comment_content":"举个列：硬币只有正反两面，抛硬币正面朝上的概率为50%，假如我抛了三次，结果三次正面朝下。这就违背与直觉观察，这是最初理解概率比较困惑的地方。","like_count":11,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1275061,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/74/b5/b68e3740.jpg","nickname":"黄申","note":"","ucode":"EE9AC074A322FF","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":437836,"discussion_content":"硬币正面朝上的概率为50%，这个是理论值，在实际中受到很多因素的影响。比如，这个硬币构造不够均匀，导致正面朝下的可能性更高。\n另外，假设这三次抛的事件都是独立的，那么三次正面朝下的概率仍有50% * 50% * 50% = 12.5%。\n\n所以从实验观测的角度来说，我们要抛足够多的次数，才可能获得更接近理论的值，否则偶然性太大。这些我会在后面的专栏介绍。","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1548697703,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":129206,"user_name":"Paul Shan","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1593140,"ip_address":"","ucode":"32D99989028284","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1567062623,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"48127","content":"是的","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"黄申","uid":"1275061","ctime":1567107291,"ip_address":"","comment_id":129206,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"31631833695","product_id":100021201,"comment_content":"概率论是选定模型，研究产生的数据有何特征。统计是根据数据反推模型参数。","like_count":7,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1275061,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/74/b5/b68e3740.jpg","nickname":"黄申","note":"","ucode":"EE9AC074A322FF","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_